timelineItems.comment: Alvas Powell (Portland Timbers) wins a free kick on the right wing.
Foul by Justin Morrow (Toronto FC).

Attempt missed. Liam Ridgewell (Portland Timbers) left footed shot from the left side of the six yard box is close, but misses the top left corner. Assisted by Diego Valeri with a cross following a set piece situation.

timelineItems.desc: Diego Valeri (Portland Timbers) is shown the yellow card for a bad foul.
timelineItems.title: YELLOW CARD: Diego Valeri gets the man before the ball

timelineItems.comment: Justin Morrow (Toronto FC) wins a free kick on the left wing.

timelineItems.desc: Goal!  Toronto FC 3, Portland Timbers 2. Michael Bradley (Toronto FC) from a free kick with a right footed shot to the top right corner.
timelineItems.title: GOAL: Michael Bradley’s FK bypasses the fray and bounces in
